            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli tlen neci iixco ce acahya quemman moquetztoc pan tlaltepactli, ni hueli neci quence mixtli, zo azalantic huan tzictic.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
